                <h4 class="mb-4">Description</h4>
                <p class="mb-4">Pivot is a digital health company delivering clinically-proven solutions that empower people to take control of their health. Named to Fast Company’s prestigious annual list of the World’s Most Innovative Companies for 2020, the
