                <ul class="What_list">
                    <li>Be a key driver in the expansion of Pivot as the best-in-class digital smoking cessation program with a mission to help millions of people quit smoking</li>
                    <li>Take ownership of strategy and execution of Pivot’s growth via B2B platform partnerships - developing win-win partnerships to grow Pivot business beyond direct sales.</li>
                    <li>Identify key opportunities for growth and success of partnerships, and test and learn to maximize them. Develop best practices for working with partners that can be replicated as you grow the team to serve an expanding set
