                    <li>Identify and develop strong champion/s for Pivot within partners to increase awareness and advocacy of Pivot by their sales and marketing teams. Collaborate to create incentives for partners to compel sell-through of Pivot.</li>
                    <li>Collaborate with Pivot Sales team to coordinate approach to building and managing partner client pipeline. </li>
                    <li>Collaborate with all functional areas of Pivot to ensure our marketing, product, reporting and business operations function optimally to serve our partnerships. </li>
                    <li>Conduct regular business reviews with partners to assess progress against goals and identify areas for further partnership</li>
                    <li>Lead strategy and process for bringing on new platform partners - prioritize potential partners based on joint interests / clients, operational simplicity/complexity, and potential value to the business. Create compelling joint
